This prompt instructs an AI development tool to build the Decision Templates Library for Archject, a focused approval and decision-tracking solution for design projects. The system will provide opinionated, reusable templates for common decision types (finishes, layouts, change requests) to accelerate decision creation, paired with a robust Decisions List / Content Browser, a multi-step Create/Edit Decision Page, and a Project Workspace Page. The deliverables enable canonical decision management, visual side-by-side option comparisons, automated reminders, and policy-driven approvals, all within Archject’s branding and design system.

